TestStep

public TestStep(String keyword,
                String app,
                String testCase)
         throws KDTParseException
Creates a Test Step. If the keyword is not found in the given application, the Universal class is searched.

Parameters:
keyword - The keyword to run.
app - The application to find the keyword in.
testCase - The test case ID.
logLevel - The log level.
Throws:
KDTParseException - If keyword parsing fails.
Method Detail

addArgument

public void addArgument(String arg,
                        String val)
Adds an argument for the keyword. Values beginning with a '$' are substituted with a value from the current data set at runtime.

Parameters:
arg - The name of the argument.
val - The value of the argument.

run

public void run()
         throws KDTException
Runs the keyword. Substitutes values from the data set into arguments with variable values.

Throws:
KDTException - If the keyword fails to execute and the keyword's Keyword.stopTestOnFail attribute is set to true.
